name: Carried By the Fog
description:
No matter the season, the White River brings many people across the US for its famous Trout. For me, it draws me to it for its beauty and how it wraps into the landscape in its own unique way. It is never too crowded for me which provides me a place to slow down a little and enjoy where I am at.
Just as the fog moves down the river slowly, so do I.
